oads/2024/08/LCDSoundsystem-All-Points-East-2024-afterparty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LCDSoundsystem-All-Points-East-2024-afterparty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LCDSoundsystem-All-Points-East-2024-afterparty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LCDSoundsystem-All-Points-East-2024-afterparty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/LCDSoundsystem-All-Points-East-2024-afterparty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/all-points-east">All Points East 2024</a>已宣布举办官方余兴派对，以跟进<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/all-points-east">LCD Soundsystem</a>即将在音乐节上亮相的演出。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">2024 年 Glastonbury 现场液晶音响系统：萨默塞特日落的巴利阿里幸福</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/joy-anonymous-the-kills-and-new-newdad-lead-new-names-for-lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-2024-line-up-3758128">这支纽约乐队将于 8 月 23 日星期五在伦敦东部的维多利亚公园登顶</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/lcd-soundsystem-points-east-review-2325882">此前曾在 2018 年的活动中担任过头条新闻</a>。支持将来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixies">Pixies</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kills">The Kills</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newdad">NewDad</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/floating-points">Floating Points</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>等公司。</p><p>今天（8 月 9 日），APE 组织者已确认 LCD 粉丝可以在哈克尼标志性的飞蛾俱乐部（位于维多利亚公园附近）继续举办派对。这个可容纳 150 人的场地将于晚上 10 点至凌晨 3 点期间举办<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mermaid-chunky">Mermaid Chunky</a> （现场）、Idjut Boys 和 DFADJAYs 的演出。</p><p>所有 Points East 持票人均可从下周一（8 月 12 日）下午 6 点开始预售 LCD 余兴派对。特卖将于周二（13日）同时进行。<a href="https://www.allpointseastfestival.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此购买门票</a>。</p><p> LC